JSC "Rostovaeroinvest" recognized the German company Assmann Beraten + Planen as the winner of the tender for the choice of the general designer of the facility.
The sum of the contract in "RostovAeroinvest" is not disclosed.
According to the press service of OAO, nine Russian and foreign companies participated in the competition, under the terms of the tender, the project should be prepared and sent to state expertise in the spring of 2014.
The winner will have to design a new passenger terminal of the airport, as well as infrastructure facilities, internal roads and elements of improvement of the airport complex.
