The main terminal building is designed by the idea of an air bridge between Rostov-on-Don and other cities of the world.
Assmann Beraten + Planen has experience in the implementation of major projects, the company designed terminals C and E terminals Sheremetyevo International Airport and a new airport complex at the international airport "Knevichi" in Vladivostok.
Yuzhny International Airport Complex will be built in Aksai district of Rostov region and will replace the current Rostov airport, which will be closed and in the future integrated into urban development.
The construction of the air terminal complex is scheduled for 2014, the commissioning of all facilities - for 2017.
